00:37:12,645 --> 00:37:13,855
Kita harus kembali.

596
00:37:14,939 --> 00:37:16,691
- Lepaskan!
- Tidak! Jangan!

597
00:37:16,775 --> 00:37:18,735
- Lepaskan!
- Hei, dengarkan aku!

598
00:37:19,861 --> 00:37:21,696
Kita tak bisa kembali ke sana!

599
00:37:24,574 --> 00:37:25,825
Byung-ju!

600
00:37:29,704 --> 00:37:31,998
07P 4295

601
00:37:36,795 --> 00:37:38,505
Byung-ju, sadarlah.

602
00:37:42,342 --> 00:37:43,468
Aku harus kembali.

603
00:37:43,551 --> 00:37:45,136
Kau menyetir sambil mabuk.

604
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:48,306
Jika anak itu mati, kau akan dipenjara.

605
00:37:48,389 --> 00:37:50,099
