615
00:38:36,729 --> 00:38:37,730
Tidak.

616
00:38:38,398 --> 00:38:40,400
Aku mau menjenguk Yeong-chang
di rumah sakit.

617
00:38:40,483 --> 00:38:41,734
Baik, Pak.

618
00:38:46,239 --> 00:38:48,616
- Jeon Ye-seul!
<i>- Jawab pertanyaanku.</i>

619
00:38:49,325 --> 00:38:52,537
Apa ayahmu menyuruhmu
untuk mengajariku bersaksi palsu?

620
00:38:52,620 --> 00:38:54,747
Jangan seret ayahku.

621
00:38:54,831 --> 00:38:57,041
Dia akan segera memimpin negara ini.

622
00:38:57,125 --> 00:38:57,959
<i>Maka dari itu,</i>

623
00:38:58,626 --> 00:39:00,587
dia juga mencoba mengendalikanku?

624
00:39:01,421 --> 00:39:03,840
