626
00:39:06,551 --> 00:39:07,594
<i>Jaga dirimu.</i>

627
00:39:10,430 --> 00:39:11,890
Hei.

628
00:39:11,973 --> 00:39:14,142
Hei! Sialan!

629
00:39:14,225 --> 00:39:15,184
Berengsek!

630
00:39:26,070 --> 00:39:30,199
Komite disiplin telah membuat keputusan.

631
00:39:32,619 --> 00:39:36,539
Kemenanganmu di kontes itu
tak memengaruhi proses penerimaanmu.

632
00:39:37,415 --> 00:39:39,375
