Selamat menikmati.

762
00:47:05,446 --> 00:47:06,322
Ayo makan.

763
00:47:07,323 --> 00:47:09,366
Kudengar kau tak pernah
makan bersama muridmu.

764
00:47:09,950 --> 00:47:11,535
Kau bukan muridku lagi.

765
00:47:12,787 --> 00:47:13,746
Benar.

766
00:47:14,538 --> 00:47:16,499
Aku dikecualikan secara permanen.

767
00:47:17,541 --> 00:47:18,375
Aduklah.

768
00:47:21,629 --> 00:47:23,839
